      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes sense. but for a high-end brand, we need more specifics than just \"respect customs.\" i want to establish what a \"gold standard\" of sophistication actually looks like. if a client is walking into a top-tier boardroom in London, NYC, or Dubai, what are the core pillars of dress, body language, and dining etiquette that define a truly polished professional? like, what's the actual standard?",
